title: We're So in Love With This Special Pup Named Picasso
text:
Picasso is a corgi-dachshund mix that was born with a goofy little smile. He's a happy and healthy pup and his face doesn't give him problems except for a few teeth that will have to be removed. He and his brother are being well taken care of by the folks at Luvable Dog Rescue and they'll be up for adoption soon!
